We got so many questions from you guys! Thanks for your participation! 🥲 we got a lot of similar questions so we had to put some of them together and change it into a video recording. This is our first time recording a Q&A session with our Eggbun Coach, so please understand why there may be mistakes.🙏
If you have any other questions, DM us anytime! And if you enjoyed the video, please let us know, and then we will continue making more of these!
Thank you for watching and see you guys in class!👍👍

Meet our new Eggbun coach: Jaekwon!
Jaekwon will be holding the Conversational Korean course!
Each week’s first lesson will start with a simple Korean dialogue through which you will be learning grammar and widely used Korean expressions!

Eggbun School is a course with daily lessons held trough the Eggbun Education app, daily assignments and your Eggbun Coach’s daily feedback on your homework.
Once in two weeks, you will have a phone call lesson with your coach to practice your speaking and pronunciation 🤗

Hope you will have fun learning Korean with Jaekwon and Eggbun School!
Can’t wait to see you in class!

✅ Check out the link in bio for more details on this class (price, curriculum, class details)

The application for the new semester of Real-life Korean with Sehee is open! This class focuses not only on essential grammar points but also on learning everyday Korean expressions. You will learn how to introduce yourself, or even how to schedule a meet-up with your friend. Such phrases really help to prepare for your travel or even a long-term stay in Korea 😉
Let’s study Korean together!

Check out the link in bio for more details (price, curriculum, etc.)
